article.description: — Dischon Thomas scored 14 points, Isaiah Rivera added 12 and Colorado State cruised to a 78-42 win over San Jose State on Saturday.
article.headline: Thomas, Rivera lead Colorado State past San Jose State 78-42
article.linkText: Thomas, Rivera lead Colorado State past San Jose State 78-42
article.story: SAN JOSE, Calif. -- — Dischon Thomas scored 14 points, Isaiah Rivera added 12 and Colorado State cruised to a 78-42 win over San Jose State on Saturday. Isaiah Stevens scored 10 points for Colorado State (13-1, 3-1 Mountain West). Omari Moore led San Jose State (7-7, 0-2) with 15 points. Josh O’Garro scored 10 points. ------
